Class ClientApplication

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • client.ClientApplication

  • public class ClientApplication
extends javafx.application.Application
    The ClientApplication is the main Watchneighbours client application class, which manages to launch application's windows and contains the main method
